cdata.name: RiptideCoin
cdata.desc:
Riptide project aims to ease the implementation of electronic payments for the Dispensary and Delivery services of the Marijuana industry. In order to be able to do that Riptide team will leverage the Ethereum blockchain to provide a platform that will support the transactions.

Riptide token (RIPT) is an ERC-20 token that will be used as a medium of exchange on the platform.
